<i>noun</i>: 회유 [회유/훼유], 유화 [유화] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>회유 [회유/훼유]</dt><br>
<dd>conciliation; appeasement; coaxing</dd><br>
<dd>어르고 달래어 시키는 말을 듣도록 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of persuading and enticing a person into doing something.</dd><br>
<dt>유화 [유화]</dt><br>
<dd>appeasement</dd><br>
<dd>상대방을 너그럽게 받아들여 사이좋게 지냄.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of generously accepting someone and getting along.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>